For more tutorials on using your new wallet - sending,

159
00:05:05,259 --> 00:05:07,145
receiving, and keeping your funds secure - check out the

160
00:05:07,145 --> 00:05:09,031
other guides in this series.

161
00:05:09,031 --> 00:05:10,918
You just took your financial future into your own hands.

162
00:05:10,918 --> 00:05:12,804
That's not nothing.

163
00:05:12,804 --> 00:05:14,691
That's everything.

164
00:05:14,691 --> 00:05:16,577
Welcome aboard.
